        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": true,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Information",
        "text": "<h2>Product Information</h2><ul><li>Quick, 3-minute fully personalized LED mask</li><li>Clinically studied LED wavelengths shown to improve skin’s firmness and texture</li><li>5 light wavelengths including 415nm (Blue), 605nm (Amber), 630nm (Red), 660nm (Deep Red), 880nm (Infrared)</li><li>Choose from 3 treatment modes: Skin Rejuvenation, Skin Clearing, or custom treatment via the app</li><li>Wireless, hands-free operation</li><li>Pairs perfectly with your skincare routine to boost absorption and results</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
