        "text": "<h2>Usage Instructions</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>Box out, mask on! To get started with your first treatment, you’ll need the following:</p><ul><li>Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask</li><li>Adjustable head strap (provided)</li><li>Eye protection goggles (provided)</li></ul>",
